net.joala.testlet
Class ToStringTestlet<T>

java.lang.Object

      net.joala.testlet.ToStringTestlet<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Testlet
public class ToStringTestlet<T>
extends AbstractTestlet<T>

Tests some requirements for the toString() method. See the test methods for the tested requirements.

Failures of the ToStringTestlets are most of the time results of refactorings to variable names so that the toString output does not refer to a variable name anylonger.

Since:
10/4/12
